{"tid":2099061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7.11-12 初選】政府打壓初選 票站義工做好「被拉」準備 冀民主派勿再「嘥票」","createTime":"2020-07-08T03:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T02:08:35.000Z","uid":20558,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"98ba180b96d5a009ed5f7b05e5106df560999fa9","tid":2099061,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"但在《國安法》之下，「紅線」不斷伸延，政府已開始打壓，昨警告議員若借辦事處做票站，不會獲發薪酬，初選能否成功舉行也是未知數。劉先生承認，感受到《國安法》下，人人自危，但強調會堅守信念，不會因為政權打壓而禁制自己，「作為被打壓的一群，做得到嘅就應該做」；就算作為義工，<span style=\"color: red;\">他也作好「出門口就會俾人拉」的心理準備，強調不會因未知數而卻步：「一日我覺得仲可以行一步，我都會去做我應該要做（的事）。」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/DAINOZPX3W7WE7DMJZOFPPLIKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FDAINOZPX3W7WE7DMJZOFPPLIKM%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=d6736e1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FDAINOZPX3W7WE7DMJZOFPPLIKM%2F&h=da8a4034\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/DAINOZPX3W7WE7DMJZOFPPLIKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人7.11-12 無論支持咩陣營都要出嚟投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1965b919fb4eab4ade2b5df12ed1d31382bf8fe6","tid":2099061,"uid":20558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"關於初選資訊<br />\n<br />\n7.11-12 初選票站List出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ba023416a9c5d7622593153cec8bf27cf354ae4","tid":2099061,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62270bb4f6c1fcc1a24e11a3a544e93ba7a70a78","tid":2099061,"uid":293307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"初選要出黎